TAIWAN: Taiwan 15-yr T$30 bln bond yield at 6.172 pct.Taiwan 15-yr T$30 bln bond yield at 6.172 pct.Taiwan's central bank, on behalf of the Finance Ministry, said it auctioned T$30 billion in 15-year government construction bonds on Tuesday with an average yield of 6.172 percent.  The range of the bids was between 6.160 and 6.176 percent.The coupon rate on the bonds was set at 7.10 percent. Total demand was T$113.15 billion, the official said.-- Taipei Newsroom (2-5080815)